  <brief_title>Study Comparing One Versus Two Cortisone Injections for Trigger Finger</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized Study Comparing One vs. Two Cortisone Injections for Trigger Finger</official_title>
  <sponsors>
